attributes.name: @ember-data/store/configure
attributes.description:
Provides a configuration API for the reactivity system
that WarpDrive should use.

@ember-data/store/configure.description:
Configures the signals implementation to use. Supports multiple
implementations simultaneously.
@ember-data/store/configure.name: setupSignals

params.name: buildConfig
params.description: - a function that takes options and returns a configuration object
